description: YouiDraw Logo Creator is a free, web-based program that allows you to create vector logos. You can create logos from scratch or use any of Logo Creator's many user-created templates to get started.

If you want to download an in-process logo design to your computer, so you can maintain a local copy of that logo, you can select File â†’ Download to Local Disk . This saves your current logo design project as a YLC file.
